    "We report the full results obtained by replicating Deng et al. 's experiments with both their Eyettention and our ScanEZ; in addition, we detail our ablation analyses, as well as our experiments on EML, a dataset that is not used in Deng et al. (2023): scanpath prediction performance on CELER L1 is in Table 3, broken down by the three settings of Text, Part and P.T."
